cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is about generating natural language descriptions for images and videos, which falls under the intersection of computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also heavily relies on recurrent neural networks and adversarial training, which are common techniques in natural language processing and machine learning, respectively. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are also likely categories.
